summary: An ordinance relating to the Eminent Domain proceedings for the condemnation appropriation and taking of certain land and other property bounded by Fauntleroy Avenue, Forty-seven Avenue Southwest and West Fontanelle Street, for Park and Playfield purposes, pursuant to Ordinance No. 48914 providing for the rejection of the awards has therein for the discontinuance of such proceedings and for the repealing of Ordinance No. 48914.
committee: Parks and Public Grounds and Finance
